Author: i-see-monsters
Text: Don't know about just the peel, but one(1) cucumber is only around 50 for the whole thing. Usually the peel of fruits and veggies is a little higher in calories, than the rest, but depending on how much you have eaten, I would say a maximum of 30 cals for the peel of a whole cucumber
